        "text": "=Analyze this civic complaint and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nComplaint:\n{{$json.body.description}}\n\nReturn format:\n{\n\"issueType\": \"\",\n\"department\": \"\",\n\"priority\": \"\"\n}\n\nPossible departments:\n\n* Garbage\n* Water\n* Roads\n* Electricity\n* Sewage\n* Trees\n* Traffic\n\nPriority values:\n\n* Low\n* Medium\n* High\n* Emergency\n",
